Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨姆杀了少女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了向耀眼的银河世界进发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.60,0:01:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将少女鲜红的血注入了船的引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.15,0:01:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果 萨姆爱上的不是少女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是对银河世界的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.18,0:01:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱的少女从一开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.33,0:01:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不过是装点旅行道路的花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.27,0:01:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船载着萨姆 驶向了银河世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而萨姆很快发觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.92,0:02:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他曾经那样憧憬银河世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 那里的星辰和生他养他的鱼之星球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有多大的不同？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼之星球也是银河里的一颗星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河并非遥远的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨姆从一开始就是那璀璨世界的住人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.52,0:02:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 萨姆又是为了什么杀了少女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事真的就此结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的故事我听够了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很拘谨哎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不拘谨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拘谨啦 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前天晚上 谢谢你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在教室里说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我就是很想道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必客气 我只是随性而行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 须方君…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:04:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君 明知自己说不定会死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是驯化了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是觉得不舒服 回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 很拘谨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直硬邦邦的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉须方君好冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天他们俩一起请假也不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是发生了什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.90,0:04:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们三个都是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为前天拓人君和扬卷同学约会了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:04:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉你们三个之间都好拘谨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个…我也有份吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想找死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拘谨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团总会现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 驯化了Samekh的进藤须方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从沉眠中觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Samekh（柱）的驭星者终于诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而Samekh本体的全貌还未得以确认
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使他拥有强力的第1阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不敌能够驱动素体本身的第2阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划无需改变
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:06:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒Tauburn就能当首领的规则也不变吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.37,0:06:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规则不变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有必要重新考虑我方的战术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好认为进藤须方和那个津名志拓人是同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有可能在素体的战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用进藤须方强力的第1阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第2阶段的战斗中利用第1阶段的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这主意不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎心情不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了是谁去收买Samekh的驭星者却失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 考虑到Samekh的驭星者已觉醒的现状
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们最优先的课题是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转移至第3阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则 就赢不了Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得你这么没底气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又从你手中溜走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们本来就是自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所珍视的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是因一时的感情而放过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠都
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那礼物 要退货吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不能像以前那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过一阵子再以别的理由送他？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尺寸不太合 我想去换
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要上车我要上车
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这一招啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.87,0:08:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狐狸 小狐狸 小狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.65,0:08:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去渡船停泊场是坐这辆车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面第3个站下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去旅行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我今早还被关在一个大鸟笼中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:09:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我喜欢将我关起来的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以其实也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也说喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.49,0:09:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有这种彼此喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.14,0:09:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却无法顺利发展的关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果我还是要离开岛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人重新来过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请保重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请保重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位也请保重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相位显示器 数据中转
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择E方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ADPS启动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输入远程任务
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速模拟 在5号至8号区进行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作真卖力啊 格林教授
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彩照人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彩照人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉游刃有余呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.54,0:10:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游刃有余？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的猩红之吻也感觉莫名地游刃有余
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我重塑 排除成功
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.84,0:10:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始追踪 之后交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.37,0:10:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设定标记光束
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子的第1阶段是可以操纵吻过的男人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她亲了谁 不难猜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就见识见识她的本事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经是属于我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:15.02,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}纷纷雪花 是星星的碎屑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.18,0:11:19.13,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}将手伸向天体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:23.25,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你可曾感受到那交错的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:33.17,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}此刻一切 都在黑白之中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么严肃的表情 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和须方谈谈 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人之间的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jaguar？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕…和子大人
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我支开了虎豹姐妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那二人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了防我走出岛外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在身边随时准备杀我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有柱之印的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放出岛外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤家族 自古以来有这样的家规
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 从小孩子的时候开始就一直被监视
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子的时候开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就随身带刀？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子 说她一直在意这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说她害怕但不敢问
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没真心对过别人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是建起屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独自待在遥远的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 今天很激动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被关在岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟和子那种绝望的感觉你能明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭你这个外乡人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子她 根本没有放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子她这么说了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 绮罗星的所有素体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会全部摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子她 终有一天能离开这座岛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 和子手里的包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是给你的生日礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是明知却没有收下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:14:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诫过你别轻易对我动手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.51,0:14:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的第一阶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能会杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会喜欢或者讨厌一个人到想杀他的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有关心过我到起杀意的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 连自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实也就是放任自流而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己 和我不也是同一类人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 从遇见你那天起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一直对你抱有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知可能死还游来 是为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想骗过我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.15,0:14:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一探究竟是吗 对自己的生死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我没有真心对人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你呢 有多真心？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的拳头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.87,0:15:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动真格的话不会就那种程度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非那种程度的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就叫嚣着要保护和子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 根本无须动用王之柱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.95,0:15:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀你根本不成问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 尽管挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你知道自己有几两重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零时空间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方也在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飒爽登场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤须方已经
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为我猩红之吻一阶的俘虏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的一切都已经是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方那庞大的生命力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,填满了我的Peshent（口）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经由Samekh强化的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这台Peshent是无敌的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.51,0:17:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可有意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且津名志拓人与进藤须方是好友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.81,0:17:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况下他无法作战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.44,0:17:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击败银河美少年的是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:17:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人 须方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.33,0:18:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了 须方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.40,0:18:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？果然了得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猩红之吻的一阶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能如此完美的控制对象物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他在开动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.17,0:19:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Peshent被支配了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 这种程度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要让和子伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看错你了 须方！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把小刀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为保护和子带在身上的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够笨拙的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛上长大的乡下人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦 外乡人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人都在…笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Peshent承受不了Samekh的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生的冒险仍在继续
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.36,0:24:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新加入剧团夜间飞行的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野酱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.23,0:24:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而绮罗星十字团的新干部登场
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.59,0:24:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 驭星者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.43,0:24:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野其人的初恋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.35,0:24:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大家再见了
